                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "How do you call Zend_Translate?\r\nBecause it does only read MO files... it does not handle or read PO files.\r\n\r\nThe implementation has tests on real plural mo-files.\r\nSo my expectation is that you missed to set the proper plural rules within poedit.\r\nDetails can only be seen and said when you attach the related mo file.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
